description:
A magical fantasy & a fantastic dress up game - completely FREE & packed with 6 different mini dress up games which easily teach color identification in a fun and exciting way. Choose from a stylish variety of beautiful dresses and gowns made for a princess, choose a royal outfit to best suit the King, help Goldilocks choose the best dress for a forest stroll, dress up the 3 bears for a perfect family photo, choose the best armor to protect the kingdom, help the elves choose a magical outfit. 

Enjoy endless hours of pleasure, remarkable animation technology, through many interactive activities, colorful scenes and and wholesome family fun. 

What’s Inside - Learn colors with 6 mini-games: 
> Colors - Fun to learn recognise and pronounce 
> King & Princess Dress Up - interactive activities 
> Goldilocks & the 3 bears - interactive activities 
> Warriors & Elves - interactive activities 
> Enjoy and Learn - A beautiful assortment of colors 

CONTACT US
Let us know what you think! Questions? Suggestions? Technical Support? Contact us 24/7 at: Support@kidbabytoddler.com

IMPORTANT MESSAGE FOR PARENTS:
* This App is free to play but certain in-game items may be purchased for real money. You may restrict in-app purchases by disabling them on your device.
* By downloading this App you agree to TabTale’s Privacy Policy and Terms of Use at http://tabtale.com/privacy-policy/ and at http://tabtale.com/terms-of-use/.
Please consider that this App may include third parties services for limited legally permissible purposes.
